# procmailrc --- Deliver mail. -*- comment-start: "# "; mode: conf-unix -*-

### Environment:
SHELL=/bin/sh
MAILDIR=$HOME/posta
SENDMAIL=/usr/bin/msmtp
LOGFILE=$HOME/log/procmail.log
VERBOSE=yes
LOGABSTRACT=yes
DROPPRIVS=yes

### Rules:
#### Spam check:
:0fw
| /usr/bin/spamc

# Discard if spam-score â‰¥ 10 stars.
:0
* ^X-Spam-Level: \*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*\*
/dev/null

# Put into spam mailbox otherwise.
:0:
* ^X-Spam-Status: Yes
spam

### Delivery:
# Deliver non-spam messages.
:0:
